    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1.0 across all operating points with NRMSE within acceptance band. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: validation runs were executed under build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2; the production build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7 differs only in license-server handling per vendor release notes, and the validation evidence is considered applicable without re-execution.",
